.TH "comedi_isadma_disable_on_sample" 9 "comedi_isadma_disable_on_sample" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
comedi_isadma_disable_on_sample \- disable the ISA DMA channel
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "unsigned int" comedi_isadma_disable_on_sample
.BI "(unsigned int dma_chan "  ","
.BI "unsigned int size "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dma_chan" 12
the DMA channel to disable
.IP "size" 12
the sample size (in bytes)
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns the residue (remaining bytes) left in the DMA transfer.
